<HL>
   NL Industries Sues
   Lockheed, Seeking
   To Nullify Election
   ----
   By Karen Blumenthal
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
04/19/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A8
</SO>
